<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Data Export is Ready - Flotilla</title>
  <style>
    /* Flotilla Brand Colors: Blue (#3b82f6) + Yellow (#eab308) */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
      padding: 50px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #dbeafe;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4b5563;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #eff6ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .info-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #1e40af;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .info-box p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #1f2937;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #eab308;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .warning-box p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #78350f;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eab308 0%, #f59e0b 100%);
      color: #1f2937;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.4);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .footer-brand {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #3b82f6;
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #e5e7eb;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üì¶ Your Data Export is Ready!</h1>
      <p>Your personal data is ready to download</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hello <strong>{{username}}</strong>! üëã</p>

      <p class="message">
        Your GDPR data export request has been processed successfully. Your personal data is now ready to download from a secure location.
      </p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>üìã Export Information</h3>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> Completed</p>
        <p><strong>Format:</strong> Your data is available in the format you requested</p>
        <p><strong>Expires:</strong> {{expiresAt}} (7 days from completion)</p>
      </div>

      <p class="message">
        Your export includes:
      </p>
      <ul style="color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8; margin: 15px 0;">
        <li>User profile and account information</li>
        <li>Organization and team memberships</li>
        <li>Projects and repositories</li>
        <li>Issues, pull requests, and code reviews</li>
        <li>Comments and activity logs</li>
        <li>Notifications and audit logs</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="{{downloadUrl}}" class="cta-button">Download Your Data</a>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <p>
          <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> This download link will expire in 7 days for security reasons. Please download your data before {{expiresAt}}.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p class="message" style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        <strong>üîí Privacy & Security:</strong> Your data export is stored securely and will be automatically deleted after expiration. The download link is unique and can only be accessed by your account.
      </p>

      <p class="message" style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        If you have any questions about your data export or need assistance, please contact our privacy team.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        <span class="footer-brand">Flotilla</span> - We build consensus<br>
        Distributed Code Hosting Platform
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
        ¬© 2025 Flotilla. All rights reserved.<br>
        GDPR Compliant Data Export
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
